01:08:50,050 --> 01:08:55,750
We finished the 300 gram and
we ordered another 300.

432
01:08:59,049 --> 01:09:05,949
By the time the meze snack came we are
in the middle of the second bouts

433
01:09:06,553 --> 01:09:12,852
which was about 150
grams to each one.

434
01:09:19,152 --> 01:09:23,949
The meze snack came and by the
time we started eating the meze

435
01:09:24,549 --> 01:09:35,650
because we were not used to drinking this
little wine made us all totally drunk.

436
01:09:46,149 --> 01:09:58,750
I remember that when the waiter came
to be paid to make the account,

437
01:10:02,353 --> 01:10:17,952
the bill was 38 drachmas. We
had a note of 100 drachmas.

438
01:10:20,949 --> 01:10:33,254
The bill was less than 50 percent so we were
so drunk that one of us gives the 100 drachmas

439
01:10:33,849 --> 01:10:49,752
and the waiter was about to give us the
change. One of us says keep the change.

440
01:10:55,753 --> 01:11:06,249
In the meantime I wanted to say 'no it
is too much' but I was laughing so much

441
01:11:06,854 --> 01:11:20,649
that I could not talk. The waiter
waited... this is my chance...

442
01:11:23,951 --> 01:11:29,649
For a long time I could not say this
is too much, they could not realize.

443
01:11:30,854 --> 01:11:35,349
I was the only one who could
realize but I could not speak.

444
01:11:37,152 --> 01:11:38,353
It was impossible.

445
01:11:38,954 --> 01:11:50,051
Anyhow the waiter understood that and he gave
the change and we took the bus to go home.

446
01:11:51,251 --> 01:11:58,153
In the bus we keep on
laughing all the time.

447
01:11:59,353 --> 01:12:01,751
Everybody was looking at us.

448
01:12:03,249 --> 01:12:12,249
As you know I had no parents from the age
of 11 and was living with aunts and uncles.

449
01:12:13,149 --> 01:12:26,949
I go home and I lie and my aunt looks at
me, where have you been, it's 11 o'clock?

450
01:12:29,349 --> 01:12:39,849
I pretend that I don't understand and I
go to bed and lie and the moment I lie

451
01:12:40,449 --> 01:12:54,249
all comes out and I rushed to the toilet.
I could not smell wine for 6 months.

452
01:12:58,149 --> 01:13:03,849
Even today if I drink more than
2 glasses of wine I am out.

453
01:13:05,349 --> 01:13:12,251
I cannot tolerate. But this was a
very interesting experience for me.

454
01:13:35,649 --> 01:13:41,349
I think that with such a difficult
subject we have to say some stories.

455
01:13:47,649 --> 01:13:59,053
- If I understood well. Hahnemann made a
