01:14:11,652 --> 01:14:15,849
- This is actually
confusing the whole issue.

459
01:14:24,251 --> 01:14:29,951
- We should take into consideration
that we are talking about provings.

460
01:14:35,654 --> 01:14:48,251
- He mixes the provings he had done with the
