462
01:15:01,752 --> 01:15:10,151
What you have to take into consideration
are symptoms from small doses

463
01:15:14,949 --> 01:15:25,750
and some primary symptoms that were happening
in these people who died with poisoning,

464
01:15:26,654 --> 01:15:32,651
they must have started with some
symptoms that are useful for us.

465
01:15:33,849 --> 01:15:40,751
The symptoms which are useful for
us eventually were toxic symptoms

466
01:15:41,049 --> 01:15:50,051
that have been described in cases that have
been poisoned by poisonous substances.

467
01:15:50,654 --> 01:16:00,849
Like the Rhus tox, Nux vomica, Ignatia... most
probably these drugs containing strychnine.

468
01:16:06,551 --> 01:16:16,453
They were used for poisoning.
