469
01:16:18,849 --> 01:16:26,654
- In paragraph 105, he
calls it pharmacology.

470
01:16:32,051 --> 01:16:40,149
He says we have to find out what happens
with the healing with our remedies...

471
01:16:50,953 --> 01:17:05,350
We have in Germany, a doctor who has a
book that writes about the toxicology

472
01:17:05,652 --> 01:17:17,652
and happened to people in older times with
