475
01:17:34,154 --> 01:17:41,952
But in the way that these paragraphs
are written, confusion is caused.

476
01:17:42,551 --> 01:17:48,250
Unless you really understand the spirit
of it, and not the letter of that.

477
01:17:49,750 --> 01:17:51,552
Then it comes to mind.

478
01:18:00,250 --> 01:18:11,651
If I give you 5 words, you look at
them ,do they have any meaning? No.

479
01:18:13,149 --> 01:18:25,450
Now you connect these words with some
others and the 5 words make a meaning.

480
01:18:31,752 --> 01:18:37,151
But the meaning of this
phrase is difficult.

481
01:18:38,349 --> 01:18:42,252
Not everybody will
understand what it means.

482
01:18:45,851 --> 01:18:55,187
20 people first read the words and they
mean nothing, then they are connected

483
01:18:56,049 --> 01:18:59,051
and mean something
for everybody.

484
01:19:02,349 --> 01:19:08,651
The real meaning of the phrase
was only understood only by few.

485
01:19:09,851 --> 01:19:26,249
By whom was the meaning understood? By those who
had it already in their spirit, in their mind.

486
01:19:29,551 --> 01:19:38,553
I will tell you a word, freedom.
Tell me, what it means for you.

487
01:19:39,450 --> 01:19:47,550
For each one it has a meaning. I want
to be free to do whatever I like.

488
01:19:48,151 --> 01:19:55,353
I want not to have my mother
or father say anything...

489
01:20:01,351 --> 01:20:08,549
Each one understands the word
freedom in a different way.

490
01:20:16,952 --> 01:20:28,951
Which is the real freedom? I
don't want dictatorships.

491
01:20:35,850 --> 01:20:41,850
Is this the meaning of
freedom in its real sense?

492
01:20:45,754 --> 01:20:52,651
Can anybody take away my freedom
because he is a dictator?

493
01:20:53,849 --> 01:20:59,551
Yes they can, because if I speak
against them they will put me in jail.

494
01:21:00,753 --> 01:21:02,554
That is one meaning.

495
01:21:05,251 --> 01:21:13,652
If you think more about it
more, what is to be free?

496
01:21:18,753 --> 01:21:29,252
These are the considerations that made
me write the definition of health

497
01:21:31,651 --> 01:21:45,150
as freedom from pain,
passion, egoism ...

498
01:21:45,754 --> 01:21:54,753
if you meditate upon these meanings you will
find out that my understanding of freedom

499
01:21:55,351 --> 01:22:00,151
is different than from the
understanding of a freedom fighter.

500
01:22:09,152 --> 01:22:14,553
Do they understand freedom
the way I do? No.

501
01:22:15,152 --> 01:22:28,052
Who is right? Who has real freedom?
I'll give some examples.

502
01:22:33,449 --> 01:22:44,249
You have an affair with a woman,
you are very attached to her,

503
01:22:45,450 --> 01:22:55,952
your whole life depends on that woman, you
want her to be happy and always with you.

504
01:23:02,551 --> 01:23:07,651
Do you believe that such
a person is free? No.

505
01:23:08,553 --> 01:23:13,052
He depends entirely on what
the other person will say.

506
01:23:14,251 --> 01:23:28,351
Even the least comment can make the
other person totally desperate

507
01:23:30,150 --> 01:23:39,449
because the person you love said you are
this or that is enough to destroy you.

508
01:23:40,652 --> 01:23:47,253
Therefore you depend your life,
happiness on that person.

509
01:23:48,152 --> 01:23:54,151
The moment you are with the person you are
very happy as long as you are together.

510
01:23:55,351 --> 01:24:07,051
When will you become free? When
you still love this person

511
01:24:08,253 --> 01:24:18,452
but are not attached to it to that degree.
You can be free at the same time.

512
01:24:19,649 --> 01:24:28,653
You have love for this person,
these are good feeling.

513
01:24:31,351 --> 01:24:37,050
The moment that you are
attached that is a passion.

514
01:24:37,353 --> 01:24:39,751
I want this woman
nobody will touch her.

515
01:24:40,654 --> 01:24:52,952
Like all the Lachesis cases like
to keep their passion/relation,

516
01:24:54,151 --> 01:25:00,151
not to be touched by
the other gender.

517
01:25:01,052 --> 01:25:10,351
The moment Lachesis sees the husband
greeting a woman... looks at the hands

518
01:25:10,953 --> 01:25:28,652
how much they touch... that is attachment.
Then you are not free.

519
01:25:28,953 --> 01:25:37,952
If you love but at the same time you
can say she is free. She can go.

520
01:25:40,050 --> 01:25:43,351
Then there is love and freedom.

521
01:25:44,852 --> 01:25:54,751
The greatest freedom of all of course, nobody
has, is be free of the ego and the selfishness.

522
01:25:57,151 --> 01:26:02,852
We can forget that. No one
can be free of the ego.

523
01:26:08,554 --> 01:26:17,851
Some people have given up their ego
quite a lot but entirely? Forget it.

524
01:26:18,451 --> 01:26:20,551
There is nobody.

525
01:26:21,751 --> 01:26:32,554
Do not aspire to be free of egotism because
the moment you are totally free of egotism

526
01:26:33,152 --> 01:26:43,951
you will be connected to the next world and you
will live in paradise but not in this world.

527
01:26:44,253 --> 01:26:49,951
You will be in the next
world, it will be very nice.

528
01:26:55,952 --> 01:27:07,351
So all spiritual attainments drive towards
the elimination of this ego centered sense.

529
01:27:08,849 --> 01:27:13,051
That is the spiritual
driving of all persons.

